Subject: [EVP-ITC] Not to be a wet blanket



But ,

yesterday I posted like 20 files and did not recieve one reply on any 
of them.

Yet a post about a broken cell phone recieves a hundred replies.
What is this group about?

Frank is right what the hell is the sense of posting files to an EVP-ITC
group if no one pays attention to the evp&#39;s or files that are posted.

I admit I do not reply to every single post myself but I do try and 
reply to most.

If no one is even bothering to listen to the files you are really 
missing what this is all about.

Come o9n guy&#39;s this is supposed to be about the exchange of ideas and 
constructive suggestions on evp-itc research. It&#39;s not a chat board or 
a forum for personal vendeta&#39;s

Let&#39;s get with the program and do some evp work.

And I&#39;ll bet I get some replies to this post that&#39;s for sure !

Bruce




